imdb.plot outline: Master Pilates instructor Mari Winsor targets your midsection and core. Strengthen your powerhouse and get a smaller waist, flatter abs and a longer, leaner look. Flat Abs Pilates Workout features over 17 abs-sculpting moves sequenced to give you a core conditioning burn.
